eye-wig
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number: 1
Definition:to remove the wool from around the eyes and head of sheep [to prevent woolblindness and blindness where seeds become stuck in wool around the eyes, inflaming and infecting them.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
